snippet.textDisplay: As a Brit, I feel disrespected. Our beautiful pies have either been manipulated with the addition of too much meringue or forgotten about entirely by the American public. You open a pie shop and you don’t think to do your cultural research. Where is the steak & ale pie, chicken & mushroom pie, pork pie, lamb shank pie, fish pie, cottage pie, shepherds pie. Also, just a side note: NEVER EAT A SLICE OF A GIANT MINCE PIE. Mince pies are meant to be small like cupcakes and you eat one or two.
